Tonight Kennedy does her monologue on the Confederate flag.

ANN COULTER is in studio to be interviewed. They start talking about the Confederate flag. Then they move on to fighting about Ann's book "Adios America" and her opinion on immigration. Kennedy is pro. Ann is anti-. An entertaining fight ensues. 

Tonights panel consists of JAMIE WEINSTEIN, JIMMY FAILLA, KAYLEIGH McENANY. They kick it off talking about the seemingly inevitable nomination of Hillary Clinton.

The panel returns to talk about Puff Daddy aka Diddy attacking his kids coach with a kettle bell and goes to jail.

Our panel is back to discuss the politics of self control. Trump "surging" in New Hampshire. 

HOLLY MADISON is here to talk about her new book "DOWN THE RABBIT HOLE". Inside the Playboy mansion.
